$choices = @(\"Yes\", \"No\")\n    $defaultChoice = if ($Default -eq \"Y\") { \"Yes\" } else { \"No\" }\n    \n    $result = Get-UserChoice -Prompt $Prompt -Choices $choices -Default $defaultChoice\n
